{"tid":967315,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【蘋果危機】內地客揸新iPhone：下一部會轉用華為","createTime":"2019-01-03T11:50:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-03T13:06:35.000Z","uid":78546,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"51342512be4ab72924c2ce2f767b8d57ad78e354","tid":967315,"uid":78546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T11:50:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190103&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=59100424\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190103%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D59100424&d=fKH14PBUn4xEMhEcuLN8vLr9WXPazFMcT8p8rn878U0%3D&h=93724f4c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190103%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D59100424&h=29cb06e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190103&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=59100424</a> <br />\n<br />\n蘋果發表業績預警，行政總裁庫克（Tim Cook）接受CNBC訪問時透露，收入不如預期主要受到中國需求放緩影響，以及手機升級換代也不如預期強勁。<br />\n<br />\n記者來到銅鑼灣希慎門市查看，發現店內人流不俗，不少市民及遊客到店內試用手機，暫未見人流有放緩跡象，但真正購買的客人不算多。<br />\n<br />\n手持新款iPhone中國遊客金芳表示，受早前華為事件影響，身邊的朋友都轉用華為手機。她坦言下一部都會考慮轉用，「要支持國貨」。<br />\n<br />\n至於馬鞍山居民鄧先生透露現時使用iPhone5，「用咗咁耐都未壞」，他直指現時新iPhone太貴，功能轉變亦不大，近年加價太「兇狠」，沒有太大意欲換機，「新嘅要去到4、5千蚊先叫合理。」"},{"pid":"36a970a9565e63f108c17e4307b5c6b2c5ef5a93","tid":967315,"uid":199725,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T11:51:37.000Z","msg":"華為可成最大贏家"},{"pid":"9c408c144fff59496ea2fa978bc393da68e71d85","tid":967315,"uid":125128,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T11:56:40.000Z","msg":"5位數 或者接近<br />\n其實都真係幾過份<br />\n要去返7-8k(最高配置）就差唔多"},{"pid":"e39702d7fbcfba5f653fe04803d6c82eaf9b43a0","tid":967315,"uid":133375,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T11:58:53.000Z","msg":"華為仲有冇下一部？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fabe98a32f1828c237f36196d85a6a9698d942af","tid":967315,"uid":61280,"like":3,